==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: able to approach within one step

===Idiom===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' yī cù kě jī)
# {{Taiwanese Mandarin}} to reach the goal in one step; do it all in one single day
#* '''2006''' ''anon'', ''[http://forum.pchome.com.tw/forum/post.php?mode=item&type=1&board=chinese_opera&subject=3559&read=1 PChome online 討論區]'' (Pchome online Message board)
#*: ''[[學習]][[過程]][[絕非]]'''一蹴可幾'''，[[甭]][[想]][[一次]][[就]][[記住]][[全部]].''
#*:: ''The learning process is not such that you can just '''do it all in one single day'''.  Don't think that you will be able to remember everything in one sitting.''

